## Dimension: Coverage

**Definition**: The proportion of substantive content from source responses that is represented in the graph.

**Why This Matters**: The Delphi process depends on capturing all expert input. Selective extraction risks privileging some voices over others, undermining the legitimacy of the scientific advice.

